# Asteria

**An open source backend made in Javascript!**

![Banner](https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/fortnite/images/9/93/Chapter_Two%2C_Season_Two_%28Full%29_-_Loading_Screen_-_Fortnite.png/)

<a href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript" target="_blank">
  <img src="https://img.shields.io/badge/written%20in-javascript-f7df1e.svg?style=for-the-badge&logo=javascript&logoColor=black" alt="Written in JavaScript" />
</a>

## Requirements

1: Install the latest [Node.JS](https://nodejs.org/en/download/current)
2: Run Start.bat (Installs Packages If You Havent Already)


# Features
- [x] Lobby Support (Tested on S7, S8 and S12)
- [X] Mobile Login Page (mobile support soon ig)
- [X] Dedicated Discord Bot
- [X] Good Auto Rotator
- [X ] Chapter 2 + Chapter 1 Support
- [X]  Base Launcher API (For Merging Launchers With Backends)




